title: RHOA Cruising Through Jamaica

description:
Danny recaps The Real Housewives of Atlanta, which featured the end of the Jamaica trip, Kandi and Marlo coming together over food, bird trouble, and a lazy river. Danny also touches on Top Gun: Maverick, and lots more!
